      • addRequestHeaderFieldStaticValue

        public long addRequestHeaderFieldStaticValue(boolean httpHeaderFieldEnabled,
                                    java.lang.String httpHeaderFieldName,
                                    java.lang.String httpHeaderFieldValue)
        Add or replace a HTTP request header field that contains a static value. Note: The header field can be replaced by passing an already configured header field name. In such a case the replaced header field will have a new ID.
        Parameters:
        httpHeaderFieldEnabled - true = sending the HTTP header field is enabled, false = disabled
        httpHeaderFieldName - the name of the HTTP header field
        httpHeaderFieldValue - the value of the HTTP header field
        Returns:
        the new ID of the HTTP request header field

      • addRequestHeaderFieldRandomValue

        public long addRequestHeaderFieldRandomValue(boolean httpHeaderFieldEnabled,
                                    java.lang.String httpHeaderFieldName,
                                    int httpHeaderFieldValueScope)
        Add or replace a HTTP request header field that contains a random value. Note: The header field can be replaced by passing an already configured header field name. In such a case the replaced header field will have a new ID.
        Parameters:
        httpHeaderFieldEnabled - true = sending the HTTP header field is enabled, false = disabled
        httpHeaderFieldName - the name of the HTTP header field
        httpHeaderFieldValueScope - the scope of the random value of the HTTP header field
        Returns:
        the new ID of the HTTP request header field
        See Also:
        AppDynamicsHTTPRequestHeaderFieldRandomValueSetup.SCOPE_NEW_VALUE_PER_TESTJOB, AppDynamicsHTTPRequestHeaderFieldRandomValueSetup.SCOPE_NEW_VALUE_PER_USER, AppDynamicsHTTPRequestHeaderFieldRandomValueSetup.SCOPE_NEW_VALUE_PER_LOOP, AppDynamicsHTTPRequestHeaderFieldRandomValueSetup.SCOPE_NEW_VALUE_PER_URL
